QuestData.Title: It's Ours Now
QuestData.Description: Only the strongest and foulest Vilebranch are left now. The soul eaters and blood drinkers, foul worshippers of the evil god Hakkar.$B$BDon't forget you're not just fighting trolls here, $n. You're fighting dark and evil forces that'll churn this land into ash if we let them live!$B$BShow no mercy!
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Vilebranch Blood Drinkers and 5 Vilebranch Soul Eaters in Jintha'Alor.
QuestData.RewardText: We've cleared straight through 'em! Jintha'Alor is as good as wiped out!
